data.description: Seldom found, this two-story townhome boasts a serene backdrop of open space. The ample kitchen offers versatility for a table area or extra storage. With generous living and dining spaces, entertaining is effortless. A private patio invites enjoyment of the outdoors across the seasons. Adding to its allure, a two-car garage provides convenience. Upstairs, the primary bedroom features a vaulted ceiling and shared bathroom access. Second-floor laundry adds practicality. Rentals are permitted, and the seller is prepared for a quick closing, selling the home as is.
